{"tid":696083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"寧願企都唔要關愛座？","createTime":"2018-06-09T18:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T18:35:15.000Z","uid":89968,"like":5,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"af92a0063d9fa7b997bb11aac3595a1e36260915","tid":696083,"uid":89968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T18:11:31.000Z","msg":"事源我搭巴士，有個中年師奶上車，有個坐關愛座既婆婆叫佢坐隔離個位：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 師奶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你坐啦，呢個批鬥座黎架，我唔坐得架（咁架車一轉彎，佢就成個身跌左過隔離）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解唔坐呀？坐啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你坐唔坐呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔坐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁咪係囉，呢個位唔坐得家嘛，連你都唔坐啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁係因為我下個站就落車<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 批鬥座黎架，我唔坐得架<br />\n<br />\n如果你係佢，你會點做？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 照坐，關愛座唔坐得架？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔坐，我唔坐批鬥座。"},{"pid":"49cd8a29808b39c4e2c1014fed0103403d870b13","tid":696083,"uid":32753,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T18:20:15.000Z","msg":"負評比樓主00後口吻"},{"pid":"08b4bf1cc2641cd44ec9048954129c22e3035c29","tid":696083,"uid":183392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T18:27:57.000Z","msg":"我係佢就坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊有人批鬥中坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係批都批後生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/10/02272